OL,7,FPolice in Northern Ireland undertook
OL,8,Fsix-monthly trawls of the phone data
OL,9,Fof "troublemaker" journalists to see
OL,10,Fif they were in contact with officer
OL,11,Fsources, a tribunal has heard.
OL,13,FDetails of what was described as
OL,14,F"Orwellian" PSNI spying tactics on
OL,15,Freporters emerged at a sitting of the
OL,16,FInvestigatory Powers Tribunal (IPT) in
