OL,7,FThe revelations were aired in the
OL,8,Flatest hearing of a case examining
OL,9,Fallegations that two investigative
OL,10,Freporters in Northern Ireland were
OL,11,Fsubject to unlawful covert
OL,12,Fintelligence by the police.
OL,14,FEvidence presented to the tribunal on
OL,15,FWednesday suggested that Police
OL,16,FService of Northern Ireland (PSNI)
OL,17,Fspying operations extended to several
OL,18,Fother reporters operating in the
OL,19,Fregion.
