OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FIn 2018, investigative documentary
OL,8,Fmakers Barry McCaffrey and Trevor
OL,9,FBirney were controversially arrested
OL,10,Fas part of a police investigation into
OL,11,Fthe alleged leaking of a confidential
OL,12,Fdocument that appeared in a film they
OL,13,Fmade on a Troubles massacre.
OL,15,FThe PSNI later unreservedly apologised
OL,16,Ffor how the men had been treated and
OL,17,Fagreed to pay #875,000 in damages to
OL,18,Fthe journalists and the film company
OL,19,Fbehind the documentary.
