OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FIn 2019, Mr Birney and Mr McCaffrey
OL,8,Flodged a complaint with the IPT asking
OL,9,Fit to establish whether there had been
OL,10,Fany unlawful surveillance of them.
OL,12,FThe PSNI had asked Durham Constabulary
OL,13,Fto take the lead in the investigation
OL,14,Finto the leaked Police Ombudsman of
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland document that
OL,16,Fappeared in the documentary, No Stone
OL,17,FUnturned, into the 1994 loyalist
OL,18,Fparamilitary massacre in the village
OL,19,Fof Loughinisland in Co Down.
