OL,7,FLast week, 600 pages of new evidence
OL,8,Fwere disclosed to the tribunal ahead
OL,9,Fof a substantive hearing scheduled for
OL,10,FOctober.
OL,12,FThose papers included a Durham
OL,13,FConstabulary minute of a meeting
OL,14,Fbetween the senior investigating
OL,15,Fofficer from Durham, Darren Ellis, and
OL,16,Ftwo PSNI detective sergeants working
OL,17,Fin intelligence operations.
