OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FBen Jaffey KC, representing Mr
OL,8,FMcCaffrey, revealed that the note made
OL,9,Freference to what was described as a
OL,10,FPSNI "defensive operation" against
OL,11,Fjournalists in the region.
OL,13,F"It appears to disclose the existence
OL,14,Fof what the PSNI call a defensive
OL,15,Foperation involving the cross-
OL,16,Freferencing of billing with police
OL,17,Ftelephone numbers on a six-monthly
OL,18,Fbasis of what appear to be a group of
OL,19,FNorthern Irish journalists who have
OL,20,Fwritten unobliging things about the
OL,21,FPSNI," he told the tribunal.
