OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe barrister said the document
OL,8,Findicated the operation was definitely
OL,9,Fin place in 2017.
OL,11,FBut he added: "We don't know when it
OL,12,Fstarted and we don't know when it's
OL,13,Ffinished and we don't know what it
OL,14,Finvolves."
OL,16,FMr Jaffey said the PSNI had yet to
OL,17,Foffer a response to the material
OL,18,Fdisclosed by Durham Constabulary.
