OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"But if this is what has been going
OL,8,Fon, we obviously say it's unlawful to
OL,9,Fgo and take a list of troublemaker
OL,10,Fjournalists, get their billing every
OL,11,Fsix months and cross-reference it with
OL,12,Fa list of police telephone numbers,
OL,13,Fand see if those journalists have got
OL,14,Fany new police sources is plainly
OL,15,Funlawful.
OL,17,F"A defensive operation can only be
OL,18,Fwhat we say is a slightly Orwellian
OL,19,Feuphemism."
