OL,7,FAs well as the events around the
OL,8,Fdocumentary, the tribunal, chaired by
OL,9,FLord Justice Singh, had also been
OL,10,Fprobing two other instances of police
OL,11,Fsurveillance against Mr McCaffrey in
OL,12,F2013 and 2011.
OL,14,FMr Jaffey said the fresh evidence
OL,15,Fdisclosed to the tribunal suggested he
OL,16,Fcould have been subjected to many more
OL,17,Fcovert spying bids.
