OL,7,FWhen the case opened in February, it
OL,8,Fheard allegations that the Met Police
OL,9,Fillegally obtained Mr McCaffrey's
OL,10,Fphone data in 2011 ` data that police
OL,11,Fin Northern Ireland subsequently
OL,12,Fsecured seven years later as part of
OL,13,Fanother probe into the reporter's work.
OL,15,FFurther claims around the Met's
OL,16,Finvolvement in accessing data from the
OL,17,Freporter were also aired at
OL,18,FWednesday's hearing.
