OL,7,FLast week, it emerged that the BBC had
OL,8,Finstructed lawyers to contact the
OL,9,Ftribunal over claims one of its ex-
OL,10,Finvestigative reporters was spied on
OL,11,Fby police.
OL,13,FThe corporation said the allegations
OL,14,Frelate to former BBC journalist
OL,15,FVincent Kearney and his work on a 2011
OL,16,FSpotlight documentary that probed the
OL,17,Findependence of the Police Ombudsman's
OL,18,Foffice.
