OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Kearney, who is the current
OL,8,FNorthern Editor at RTE, said he is
OL,9,Fdetermined to find out what happened.
OL,11,FA barrister representing the BBC was
OL,12,Fpresent in court for Wednesday's
OL,13,Fhearing. He said the corporation was
OL,14,Ftaking its intervention in the case
OL,15,F"seriously".
OL,17,FThe PSNI and other respondents in the
OL,18,Fcase have been asked to respond to the
OL,19,Fissues raised ahead of a further
OL,20,Freview hearing in July.
