OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FOutside the Royal Courts of Justice
OL,8,Fafter the sitting adjourned, Mr Birney
OL,9,Fsaid the hearing made clear that the
OL,10,FPSNI was "absolutely obsessed with
OL,11,Fjournalists and their sources".
OL,13,F"And I think we need to remind the
OL,14,FPSNI and remind the authorities back
OL,15,Fin Belfast that journalism isn't a
OL,16,Fcrime, that journalists all over the
OL,17,Fworld have sources and that is lawful
OL,18,Fand that is absolutely what
OL,19,Fjournalists are there to do," he added.
