OL,7,F"But what we've heard this morning is
OL,8,Fincredibly worrying about the
OL,9,Findustrial harvesting of journalists'
OL,10,Fphone data and I think that that is
OL,11,Fsomething that we really need to find
OL,12,Fout more about and we need to find out
OL,13,Fquickly.
OL,15,F"The PSNI have a duty of candour to
OL,16,Fthis court in order to explain
OL,17,Fproperly rather than being dragged to
OL,18,Fthis court kicking and screaming,
OL,19,Fwhich is what's been going on here for
OL,20,Ffive years."
